-The usual,- Prowl thinks back to Iron Raptor, looking around so she would be able to see the chaotic battle through his eyes. He looks back at Fireblade to see if the missiles he had fired hit.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
> 
> Hotmail is screwing my posts around and delaying all other ones!
> 
> * Iron Raptor sighed in annoyance as Megatron leaned in closer to the
> screen, wondering just who he though he was fooling?
> < Talk?> she though to herself, even though she wanted to say it more then 
> ever. Since when did a Predacon just want to talk?
> She crossed her arms and growled.*
> 
> " Megatron, have you ever heard of the two words ' Bite Me'? If you wanted 
> to be pleasent you'd be here in person, so stop folling around and either 
> get to the point or get lost."
> 
> * Those were her words and she was sticking to them.
> She glaced at Epyon before looking back to the screen, sensing things
> brewing outside.
> < What's the status outside?> she asked Prowl, giving him a visual hint of 
> what was happening in the controle room.
> It had been a while since they just talked because they felt like it.
> Something was always going on and they never had any time anymore.*
